metadata.name: Probably Fall
metadata.description:
-Do you see fall outside the window?  
-Yes.  
-Does it make you sad?  
-Yes.  
-Autumn is not a bad time. And it's cold on purpose so that people give each other more hugs to keep warm...

1/1  
4000x5000 px  
300 dpi  
Artist: Iri Kis

Created in a unique author's technique of combining digital watercolor, oil and volumetric textures.
